data.description:
Welcome  to the perfect place to call home. This  well maintained spacious home offer 3 bedrooms with 2 full baths, walkin closets, vauled ceiling in the master bedroom. Kitchen offers a Bay area for breakfast dining as well as a large breakfasy bar. Kitchen is fully equipped with microwave over the stove. Turn Off all Lights. PLEASE LOCK ALL DOOR LOCKS.  

Air Condition replaced in 2019. Roof replaced in 2019. New water heater 2024.
Closing by Prestige Settlement & Title Services LLC, 795 Ontario St Jacksonville, Fl 32254- 904-371-9877gh back yard for gatherings outside.
